0.1.name: wordpress/disable-upgrade-reminder
0.1.description: Disable upgrade reminder is a plugin that disables the upgrade reminder at the top of the WordPress interface for all users except administrators. It is useful for any situation when you don't want anybody except admins worrying about available updates.
